# Aqarify — End-to-End Platform Revision
**Full-stack audit: DB → Backend → Frontend → Arab World readiness**
*Audited: April 2026 | Covers every module, every layer*

---

## Executive Summary

The architecture is solid and Phases 0–3 are largely implemented. However there are **7 critical runtime bugs**, **12 FE↔BE contract mismatches**, **5 DB schema inconsistencies**, and the platform is **not yet production-ready for the Arab World** — Egypt-only assumptions are deeply baked in. This document covers every finding in order of severity with exact file references and code fixes.

