### H5 — No RLS policy for authenticated customers to read their own reserved/sold units

**Files:** `supabase/migrations/00025_harden_public_rls.sql`

Anon policy only exposes `status = 'available'` units. Authenticated customers with a confirmed reservation can't read their reserved unit via any RLS-aware query.

```sql
-- ✅ New policy
CREATE POLICY "units_customer_own_reserved" ON units
  FOR SELECT TO authenticated
  USING (
    EXISTS (
      SELECT 1 FROM reservations r
      WHERE r.unit_id = units.id
        AND r.customer_id = auth.uid()
        AND r.status IN ('pending', 'confirmed')
    )
  );
```

